        {
            "title": "NBA｜雷霆雙殺塞爾特人鎖季後賽資格 SGA轟34分破杜倫紀錄 豪言劍指總冠軍",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"基傑奧斯阿歷山大(白衫)攻入34分。AFP\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/5f1c12288616d73d9b6012d495376d7c/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250313/_2025031314582326380.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">基傑奧斯阿歷山大(白衫)攻入34分。AFP</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>周三NBA大戰，西岸一哥雷霆作客以118:112擊敗東岸二哥塞爾特人，鎖定今季季後賽資格。雷霆球星基傑奧斯阿歷山大(Shai Gilgeous-Alexander ，簡稱SGA)今場獨取34分，生涯為雷霆攻入超1萬分，超越杜倫(Kevin Durant)成隊史最快1萬分，而率隊雙殺綠軍後，他即矢言劍指總冠軍。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"雷霆雙殺塞爾特人。AFP\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/54053e1b0ddc31045301e036754c19f8/2025-03/AFP__20250313__2204814557__v2__HighRes__OklahomaCityThunderVBostonCeltics.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        雷霆雙殺塞爾特人。AFP\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"雷霆雙殺塞爾特人。AFP\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/bff80044e0caca21615fc36cd176cf94/2025-03/AFP__20250313__2204815474__v2__HighRes__OklahomaCityThunderVBostonCeltics.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        雷霆雙殺塞爾特人。AFP\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"基傑奧斯阿歷山大(白衫)攻入34分。AFP\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/85b6f5f0062484b919df3031a2339b1c/2025-03/AFP__20250313__2204813762__v2__HighRes__OklahomaCityThunderVBostonCeltics.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        基傑奧斯阿歷山大(白衫)攻入34分。AFP\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"基傑奧斯阿歷山大(白衫)攻入34分。AFP\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/482c5b90e2740c05f1ebaa86402e1c46/2025-03/AFP__20250313__2204813219__v2__HighRes__OklahomaCityThunderVBostonCeltics.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        基傑奧斯阿歷山大(白衫)攻入34分。AFP\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"基傑奧斯阿歷山大(白衫)攻入34分。AFP\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d3ea224b6a619e989c609060584507b3/2025-03/AFP__20250313__2204813453__v2__HighRes__OklahomaCityThunderVBostonCeltics.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        基傑奧斯阿歷山大(白衫)攻入34分。AFP\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"基傑奧斯阿歷山大(白衫)攻入34分。AFP\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/523bd15a589cd53c130b763170445d88/2025-03/AFP__20250313__2204814513__v2__HighRes__OklahomaCityThunderVBostonCeltics.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        基傑奧斯阿歷山大(白衫)攻入34分。AFP\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"基傑奧斯阿歷山大(白衫)攻入34分。AFP\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d93aa8db421dbd270f7bfdbd3298f949/2025-03/AFP__20250313__2204813637__v2__HighRes__OklahomaCityThunderVBostonCeltics.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        基傑奧斯阿歷山大(白衫)攻入34分。AFP\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>雷霆雙殺塞爾特人</h2>\n<p>本場強強對決戰況緊湊，完半場後雷霆只領先3分。第3節中段，雷霆一度拉開至12分優勢，但綠軍立即回應曾經追平，但雷霆末段再發力打出15:4攻勢，最終以118:112奏捷，今季雙殺對手，並確定取得季後賽入場券。\n\n</p><h2>SGA破紀錄豪言劍指總冠軍</h2>\n<p>SGA今場獨取全場最高的34分後，生涯為雷霆上陣368場貢獻10,018分，超越杜倫(381場)成雷霆隊史最快得1萬分的球員。領軍雙殺衛冕冠軍後，他矢言：「這是重大的勝利。因為綠軍曾做到我們正在努力做的事，在NBA沒有比這更好的考驗了，我認為我們通過了2場考驗。」\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
