        {
            "title": "元朗721｜6名非白衣人暴動罪成判囚25至37個月 其中3男不服定罪提上訴",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"尹仲明（左)和葉鑫昇（右）向上訴庭申請上訴。資料圖片\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/890fbe275ff64354e0d926954c72e8ce/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250313/_2025031315211825338.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">尹仲明（左)和葉鑫昇（右）向上訴庭申請上訴。資料圖片</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>前立法會議員林卓廷與另外6名非白衣男子在2019年「721事件」中，涉嫌在元朗港鐵站向閘外人士射水等。7人早前經審訊後被裁定暴動罪成，法官陳廣池上月底判處林卓廷監禁37個月，其中3個月與民主派初選案刑期同期執行。另外4名被告庾家豪、陳永晞、鄺浩林和楊朗各判監31個月，尹仲明和葉鑫昇則判囚28和25個月。楊尹葉3人均不服定罪，昨向上訴庭申請上訴。根據司法機構紀錄顯示，案件暫未排期。\n\n</p>\n<p>7名被告依次為47歲時任立法會議員林卓廷、40歲客戶服務主任庾家豪、42歲時任屋邨代表陳永晞、36歲註冊社工葉鑫昇、35歲廚師鄺浩林、52歲電器技工尹仲明及31歲航空公司地勤人員楊朗，均否認於2019年7月21日在港鐵元朗站大堂參與暴動。\n\n</p>\n<p>案件編號：CACC 54/2025\n\n</p>\n<p>法庭記者：陳子豪<br/>\n \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2057918/即時-港聞-元朗721-6名非白衣人暴動罪成判囚25至37個月-其中3男不服定罪提上訴",
            "pub_date": "2025-03-13 15:32:24",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "俠醫丨陳豪爆父母曾想自己繼承衣鉢做醫生 笑囝囝好似Boss 張曦雯獲袁詠儀讚勤力：感謝靚靚愛錫",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"俠醫丨陳豪爆父母曾想自己繼承衣鉢做醫生 笑囝囝好似Boss 張曦雯獲袁詠儀讚勤力：感謝靚嘅愛錫\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/a96d4a872dc4b9a5201fc7dbd34fb411/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250313/_2025031315112960241.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">俠醫丨陳豪爆父母曾想自己繼承衣鉢做醫生 笑囝囝好似Boss 張曦雯獲袁詠儀讚勤力：感謝靚嘅愛錫</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>陳豪、張曦雯、劉佩玥、譚凱琪、郭柏妍、馬貫東等，到將軍澳電視城出席新劇《俠醫》造型記者會，陳豪透露劇集改編自黃天賜教授的故事，他表示有好多事需要學習，包括針灸、穴位和指壓等，最重要是學會和病人噓寒問暖，了解其感受。陳豪透露媽媽是中醫、爸爸是西醫，以前有做小助手，在媽咪的師兄弟醫館中協助拔罐和按摩等，笑言父母都想他們三兄弟繼承衣鉢，但3人都沒興趣，問到子女可有興趣繼承？陳豪笑指兒子在其咖啡店時好似Boss。陳豪透露自己也腰傷過，被媽咪針了30、40針，再配合艾灸和電療等。\n\n</p><h2>Kelly服中藥調理身體</h2>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"陳豪、張曦雯、劉佩玥、譚凱琪等，到將軍澳電視城出席新劇《俠醫》造型記者會。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/9d2257b8944745ea4f66873893ae5422/2025-03/0L6A0142.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        陳豪、張曦雯、劉佩玥、譚凱琪等，到將軍澳電視城出席新劇《俠醫》造型記者會。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"陳豪表示今齣劇集改編自黃天賜教授的故事。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8e2b1e2b17e71bc39dc3184342b16240/2025-03/0L6A0033.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        陳豪表示今齣劇集改編自黃天賜教授的故事。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"陳豪繼《企業強人》後再一次與Kelly合作。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/2bc34d88f9d56f1329b1d308e3201c4c/2025-03/0L6A0034.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        陳豪繼《企業強人》後再一次與Kelly合作。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"張曦雯透露今次演事業型女性，受痛症和慣性拗柴等困擾。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/874bcfabf431c31de4665d580762dd61/2025-03/0L6A0042.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        張曦雯透露今次演事業型女性，受痛症和慣性拗柴等困擾。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"Kelly笑言會被陳豪針灸。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/29d00ea86b157229722d1afe848545e0/2025-03/0L6A0052.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Kelly笑言會被陳豪針灸。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"黃天賜教授亦有到現場。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/447ae1f9f3119450f781669be7140f5e/2025-03/0L6A0118.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        黃天賜教授亦有到現場。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"黃天賜教授與劇中主角陳豪、張曦雯一同合影。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ac8cd2df0ca9ee318e02b9b957495c7b/2025-03/0L6A0147.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        黃天賜教授與劇中主角陳豪、張曦雯一同合影。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"黃天賜教授與劇中主角陳豪、張曦雯一同合影。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/9cae4208f982100809afe5cb87c6755d/2025-03/0L6A0149.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        黃天賜教授與劇中主角陳豪、張曦雯一同合影。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"陳豪透露媽媽是中醫、爸爸是西醫，以前曾當小助手。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c91856b8adc3dc3f312d31fa6fd708bc/2025-03/0L6A0205.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        陳豪透露媽媽是中醫、爸爸是西醫，以前曾當小助手。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"陳豪笑言父母想他們三兄弟繼承衣鉢，但3人都沒興趣。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8d4cacf0006ece3afc66f8bf7c3d95fc/2025-03/0L6A0208.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        陳豪笑言父母想他們三兄弟繼承衣鉢，但3人都沒興趣。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"提到獲袁詠儀讚勤力，張曦雯感謝靚靚嘅愛錫。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/cf552fb567fb7558e482124d8ebceef6/2025-03/0L6A0219.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        提到獲袁詠儀讚勤力，張曦雯感謝靚靚嘅愛錫。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"張曦雯與袁詠儀一起拍攝《模仿人生》。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/4f420643a8e0623cd8a3bf0f5904296f/2025-03/KK__5963_0.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        張曦雯與袁詠儀一起拍攝《模仿人生》。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<p>張曦雯笑言會被陳豪針灸，今次演事業型女性，受痛症和慣性拗柴等困擾，但很依賴西藥。張曦雯指自己最近休息得不好，被黃教授發現頸錐問題，「即時幫我啪了兩下，即時醒了！」雖然外國長大，但張曦雯指自己相信食療保健，也會依靠針灸、艾灸等，亦有服中藥作調理身體。提到另一劇《模仿人生》拍攝完成，張曦雯獲袁詠儀讚勤力，她開心表示劇組都好勤力，覺得和她合作這件事好遠，但突然又實現，大家有很多對手戲，感謝靚靚兩個多月的愛錫。<br/>\n \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2057916/即時-娛樂-俠醫丨陳豪爆父母曾想自己繼承衣鉢做醫生-笑囝囝好似Boss-張曦雯獲袁詠儀讚勤力-感謝靚靚愛錫",
            "pub_date": "2025-03-13 15:26:41",
